{"id": 1234, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于租房这件事，你最在意的点是什么？", "description": "交房租总是难免的，你最甘愿为哪一点买单？（题图来自：Christopher Corr）", "record_count": 3796, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160920165856ufis7OmB9vpDrY3X.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-09-28T03:06:38Z", "options": [{"id": 120007, "content": "独卫", "image": null, "praise_count": 549, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 484896}, {"id": 117881, "content": "房东人好", "image": null, "praise_count": 272, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 119995, "content": "买菜健身看医生远一点没关系，一定要有24小时便利店、超市、咖啡馆、私房餐厅", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 333447}, {"id": 119996, "content": "周邊環境不能髒亂差，要安全", "image": null, "praise_count": 589, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 72992}, {"id": 119999, "content": "重点是便宜房好啊！", "image": null, "praise_count": 153, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 215324}, {"id": 120001, "content": "我不喜欢和情侣合租", "image": null, "praise_count": 183, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 698279}, {"id": 120003, "content": "安全，生活方便，房东亲切", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 702853}, {"id": 120008, "content": "不管多少钱，要离工作单位近；可以小，但厨卫卧必须全且朝阳", "image": null, "praise_count": 60, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680805}, {"id": 120011, "content": "要独卫", "image": null, "praise_count": 37, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770562}, {"id": 120012, "content": "交通要便利", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 647498}, {"id": 120016, "content": "便宜，方便", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 191173}, {"id": 134400, "content": "房东房东房东", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804638}, {"id": 120064, "content": "地理位置，最好靠近公司或者学校～ 而且厕所！要！好！ ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775700}, {"id": 120065, "content": "安全，不能是一楼，要有阳光和阳台，不能和男生同一间浴室", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 325078}, {"id": 120066, "content": "我想租房", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624777}, {"id": 120322, "content": "近地铁站近健身房有独立卫生间。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 461}, {"id": 120067, "content": "啥时可以买下", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 745398}, {"id": 120323, "content": "能接触到足够的阳光", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 718197}, {"id": 120068, "content": "一个人住。", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162244}, {"id": 120324, "content": "一个人住", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773298}, {"id": 120069, "content": "一个好室友", "image": null, "praise_count": 58, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 672643}, {"id": 120325, "content": "周边治安环境好，有独立的卫生间", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315265}, {"id": 120070, "content": "社区完善，晚上不吵。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 445264}, {"id": 120326, "content": "窗户的采光", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 770572}, {"id": 120071, "content": "隔音哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227035}, {"id": 121351, "content": "交通、环境、房屋大小！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 780419}, {"id": 120072, "content": "小区安全家里干净敞亮", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 775725}, {"id": 124424, "content": "落地窗 能向阳", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796279}, {"id": 120073, "content": "只要整洁无异味", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 767893}, {"id": 120329, "content": "坐北朝南，风水极佳，施法起来效果才好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 513075}, {"id"